narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned a great deal about second language acquisition and foreign language teaching. The course helped improve my teaching ad made me become more self-aware of my successes and shortcomings as a language instructor.

I could develop my linguistics skills in order to help language student. I feel that the study and reflections of all those approaches and teaching methods gave me a clear insight about the act of learning and specially of teaching.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: No weaknesses. The course is complete, pratical, informative and very useful.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes. I think this is a genuinely helpful course if you're insteresting in having foreign language instructor in your CV. It will also help you improve as an instructor (and not just for language courses).
I would totally recommend the course!
